OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782847100
OL,3,CHonesty box owner questions business
OL,4,Cafter #1000 worth of items stolen
OL,6,FThe owner of an honesty box in
OL,7,FGuernsey questioned remaining open
OL,8,Fafter around #1000 worth of items were
OL,9,Fstolen, and the self-service system
OL,10,Fwas vandalised.
OL,12,FThe Blue Chicken House Bakery on Doyle
OL,13,FStreet in St Peter Port was broken
OL,14,Finto on Thursday 25 June, with
OL,15,Fperpetrators stealing numerous
OL,16,Fvaluable items.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
