OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782847100
OL,3,CHonesty box owner questions business
OL,4,Cafter #1000 worth of items stolen
OL,6,FThe owner, James Manger, explains: "It
OL,7,Fwas very sad. I turned up at 5:30 in
OL,8,Fthe morning, I opened the doors and
OL,9,Fwas very shocked, so I shut them and
OL,10,Ftook a step back.
OL,12,F"I then realised someone had ripped
OL,13,Fthe cash box out, stolen the camera,
OL,14,Ftaken the card payment machine, and
OL,15,Fthe battery pack that powers all of
OL,16,Fit. There's the damage side of it too,
OL,17,Fit was very disheartening."
OL,19,FHowever, James says community spirit
OL,20,Fhas encouraged him to keep his doors
OL,21,Fopen.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782847100
OL,3,CHonesty box owner questions business
OL,4,Cafter #1000 worth of items stolen
OL,6,FHe explains: "I thought about closing
OL,7,Ffor a few days and stopping, just kind
OL,8,Fof re-evaluating.
OL,10,F"But, the overwhelming community
OL,11,Fresponse, positive messages, support
OL,12,Fand people telling me how much it
OL,13,Fmeans to them, has made me rethink
OL,14,Fthat actually this is a rarity in
OL,15,FGuernsey and the community response to
OL,16,Fthat proves that people won't be
OL,17,Faccepting of this terrible behaviour."
OL,19,FWhile the honesty box will remain,
OL,20,FJames admits how it works may need
OL,21,Frethinking.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782847100
OL,3,CHonesty box owner questions business
OL,4,Cafter #1000 worth of items stolen
OL,6,FHe says: "We might have to change our
OL,7,Fsystems a little bit, and we might
OL,8,Fhave to be a bit more vigilant and put
OL,9,Fsome more security up, but we are here
OL,10,Ffor the people and the people are here
OL,11,Ffor us."
OL,13,FGuernsey Police are investigating the
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/4
